A multicenter, randomized trial comparing efficacy and safety of 
paclitaxel/capecitabine and cisplatin/capecitabine in advanced gastric cancer.

Lu Z(1), Zhang X(1), Liu W(2), Liu T(3), Hu B(4), Li W(5), Fan Q(6), Xu J(7), Xu 
