Economic Evaluation of a Catheter-Associated Urinary Tract Infection Prevention 
Program in Nursing Homes.

Hutton DW(1), Krein SL(2)(3), Saint S(2)(3), Graves N(4)(5), Kolli A(6), Lynem 
R(1), Mody L(2)(7)(8).

